                        <div id="para15" class="para" smil:begin="00:13:47.820" smil:end="00:14:04.643">Well, to be sure that this, ah, system was working, we didn't just issue the directives and hope that everything would be alright. Ah, we knew that the Vietnamese alone might do some things. But, there were an awful lot of Americans present in the <span class="tei-name tei-name-Phoenix_Program">Phoenix Program</span> Advisory Force.<div class="tei-metadata"><div id="Phoenix_Program">Phoenix Program
</div>
</div>
