                <div id="q8">
                    <div id=""><strong class="speaker q">Interviewer:</strong>
                        <div id="para23" class="para" smil:begin="00:19:57.051" smil:end="00:20:02.194">But in many cases they would be a part of the village structures just like everybody else. I mean, they weren't aliens.<div class="tei-metadata">
</div>
</div>
                    
</div>
                    <div id=""><strong class="speaker a">Colby:</strong>
