                        <div id="para68_2" class="para" smil:begin="00:47:17.480" smil:end="00:47:33.300">Now the North Vietnamese had about 7,000 soldiers in Northern <span class="tei-name tei-name-Laos">Laos</span> at that time and they reviewed, they removed exactly forty of them. Ah, leaving the remainder there. And after a month or two they began to resume the process of kicking the Lao around.<div class="tei-metadata"><div id="Laos">Laos
</div>
