                        <div id="para68_3" class="para" smil:begin="00:47:33.300" smil:end="00:47:56.333">Now <span class="tei-name tei-name-Kennedy_John_F">President Kennedy</span> at that point had a problem. Was he going to let them get away with it, with what that implied, with what they could do elsewhere in <span class="tei-name tei-name-Southeast_Asia">Southeast Asia</span>, and so forth. Was he going to send American forces back there and resume a confrontation with the <span class="tei-name tei-name-Soviet_Union_Gov">Soviet Union</span>, which would've had to have reacted in that fashion, if we had overtly sent a force back there. And he didn't want to do either of those.<div class="tei-metadata"><div id="Kennedy_John_F">Kennedy, John F. (John Fitzgerald), 1917-1963
