<h4><a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20101221233032/http://openvault.wgbh.org/catalog/org.wgbh.mla:d97fe57ad5c8fff2049f78b3fa5b2cf974019ef6" class="interview-with-richard-c-holbrooke-2-1982" onclick="var f = document.createElement('form'); f.style.display = 'none'; this.parentNode.appendChild(f); f.method = 'POST'; f.action = this.href;if(event.metaKey || event.ctrlKey){f.target = '_blank';};var d = document.createElement('input'); d.setAttribute('type', 'hidden'); d.setAttribute('name', 'label'); d.setAttribute('value', 'title'); f.appendChild(d);var d = document.createElement('input'); d.setAttribute('type', 'hidden'); d.setAttribute('name', 'results_view'); d.setAttribute('value', 'true'); f.appendChild(d);var d = document.createElement('input'); d.setAttribute('type', 'hidden'); d.setAttribute('name', 'counter'); d.setAttribute('value', ''); f.appendChild(d);var m = document.createElement('input'); m.setAttribute('type', 'hidden'); m.setAttribute('name', '_method'); m.setAttribute('value', 'put'); f.appendChild(m);var s = document.createElement('input'); s.setAttribute('type', 'hidden'); s.setAttribute('name', 'authenticity_token'); s.setAttribute('value', 'V/npOcnVZOiQnPlWQKqKjntEEs2nUCKvUhh43MBnxjU='); f.appendChild(s);f.submit();return false;">Interview with Richard C. Holbrooke [2], 1982</a></h4>
        <p>Between 1963-1966 Richard Holbrooke completed diplomatic service first as a provincial representative for the Agency for International Development (AID), then as Staff Assistant to Ambassadors Maxwell Taylor and Henry Cabot Lodge. Holbrooke talks about his work in Vietnam, the assessments he had ...</p>
