<div class="mlt">
<a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20101221233032/http://openvault.wgbh.org/catalog/org.wgbh.mla:475831226e7357447dd4a4a00d6330df165e228c"><img alt=" " src="https://web.archive.org/web/20101221233032im_/http://openvault.wgbh.org/fedora/get/org.wgbh.mla:475831226e7357447dd4a4a00d6330df165e228c/sdef:THUMBNAIL/thumbnail" width="54"/></a>
<h4><a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20101221233032/http://openvault.wgbh.org/catalog/org.wgbh.mla:475831226e7357447dd4a4a00d6330df165e228c" class="interview-with-george-w-ball-1981" onclick="var f = document.createElement('form'); f.style.display = 'none'; this.parentNode.appendChild(f); f.method = 'POST'; f.action = this.href;if(event.metaKey || event.ctrlKey){f.target = '_blank';};var d = document.createElement('input'); d.setAttribute('type', 'hidden'); d.setAttribute('name', 'label'); d.setAttribute('value', 'title'); f.appendChild(d);var d = document.createElement('input'); d.setAttribute('type', 'hidden'); d.setAttribute('name', 'results_view'); d.setAttribute('value', 'true'); f.appendChild(d);var d = document.createElement('input'); d.setAttribute('type', 'hidden'); d.setAttribute('name', 'counter'); d.setAttribute('value', ''); f.appendChild(d);var m = document.createElement('input'); m.setAttribute('type', 'hidden'); m.setAttribute('name', '_method'); m.setAttribute('value', 'put'); f.appendChild(m);var s = document.createElement('input'); s.setAttribute('type', 'hidden'); s.setAttribute('name', 'authenticity_token'); s.setAttribute('value', 'V/npOcnVZOiQnPlWQKqKjntEEs2nUCKvUhh43MBnxjU='); f.appendChild(s);f.submit();return false;">Interview with George W. Ball, 1981</a></h4>
        <p>George W. Ball served in the State Department under Presidents Kennedy and Johnson, and later as Ambassador to the United Nations. He describes the early Johnson Administration as a period of “drift” when the US was becoming increasingly involved in Vietnam, a trend Ball opposed in numerous memos...</p>
